title: Matthews: Why’s Trump Bringing Up Schwarzenegger at Prayer Breakfast?, ‘Nobody Cares!’
text:
Matthews: Why’s Trump Bringing Up Schwarzenegger at Prayer Breakfast?, ‘Nobody Cares!’ by Josh Feldman | 8:59   video 
Chris Matthews brought on a Donald Trump biographer tonight to ask why the President of the United States talked about the ratings of his old TV show and dissing its current host during the National Prayer Breakfast. 
Matthews asked Michael D’Antonio “why on God’s earth” Trump is distracting from the good news out of his administration with this trivial stuff. 
D’Antonio said that Trump never lets anything go and whenever there’s something he can compete in he always wants to brag about being the winner. 
Matthews pointed out that the ratings of The Celebrity Apprentice are “not really important to 99.999 percent of this country,” and he cried “Nobody cares!” 
Watch above, via MSNBC.
